dc_title_s: Denmark Strait, Greenland Sea, Greenland (Denmark)-east coast, Kangerlussuaq Sheet (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic/Topographic Center. "LORAN-C." "Soundings in meters." Depths shown by soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Includes glossary. Title at right foot of chart: Kangerlussuaq Sheet. Map NO.38140. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA). United States. Defense Mapping Agency. (1984). Denmark Strait, Greenland Sea, Greenland (Denmark)-east coast, Kangerlussuaq Sheet (Raster Image). LandInfo. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/bj371wn3131 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
